<main class="page-wrapper shrink grow">
    <section class="max-w-full mx-auto px-4 py-10 space-y-10">
        <!-- Header Card -->
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-dark-secondary border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-6 transition-colors duration-200">
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                    <span class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-primary-500/10 dark:bg-primary-500/20 text-primary-500 dark:text-primary-400 flex-shrink-0">
                        <svg width="25" height="23" viewBox="0 0 25 23" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path
                                d="M8.125 5C8.125 6.38071 7.00571 7.5 5.625 7.5C4.24429 7.5 3.125 6.38071 3.125 5C3.125 3.61929 4.24429 2.5 5.625 2.5C7.00571 2.5 8.125 3.61929 8.125 5ZM0.625 5C0.625 7.76143 2.86357 10 5.625 10C8.38643 10 10.625 7.76143 10.625 5C10.625 2.23857 8.38643 0 5.625 0C2.86357 0 0.625 2.23857 0.625 5ZM8.75 16.875C8.75 15.1491 7.35089 13.75 5.625 13.75C3.89911 13.75 2.5 15.1491 2.5 16.875V20H8.75V16.875ZM11.25 22.5H0V16.875C0 13.7684 2.5184 11.25 5.625 11.25C8.7316 11.25 11.25 13.7684 11.25 16.875V22.5ZM21.875 5C21.875 6.38071 20.7558 7.5 19.375 7.5C17.9942 7.5 16.875 6.38071 16.875 5C16.875 3.61929 17.9942 2.5 19.375 2.5C20.7558 2.5 21.875 3.61929 21.875 5ZM14.375 5C14.375 7.76143 16.6136 10 19.375 10C22.1364 10 24.375 7.76143 24.375 5C24.375 2.23857 22.1364 0 19.375 0C16.6136 0 14.375 2.23857 14.375 5ZM22.5 16.875C22.5 15.1491 21.1009 13.75 19.375 13.75C17.6491 13.75 16.25 15.1491 16.25 16.875V20H22.5V16.875ZM13.75 20V16.875C13.75 13.7684 16.2684 11.25 19.375 11.25C22.4816 11.25 25 13.7684 25 16.875V22.5H13.75V20Z"
                                fill="currentColor" />
                        </svg>
                    </span>
                    <div class="space-y-1">
                        <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Order a Child Panel</h1>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
                            Launch your own reseller storefront in minutes and give clients a seamless place to purchase
                            their social media campaigns.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Main Content Card -->
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-dark-secondary border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-6 sm:p-8 space-y-8 transition-colors duration-200">
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
                    If you're looking to expand your business and offer social media services, ordering a child panel is
                    a great solution.
                    With a child panel, you get your own customized website where you can resell SMM services directly
                    to your clients.
                    To get started, simply fill out the order form, choose your domain, and connect it to our platform.
                    For just $10 per month, you can manage your services efficiently and grow your business by offering
                    reliable social media solutions to a wider audience.
                    It's an easy way to increase your revenue while maintaining full control over your panel.
                </p>
                <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Fill in the form below to order your panel</h2>
            </div>

            <!-- Order Plan & Benefits -->
            <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2">
                <!-- Subscription Plan Card -->
                <div class="flex flex-col rounded-xl border-2 border-primary-200 dark:border-primary-500/30 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50/50 to-white dark:from-primary-900/20 dark:to-dark-card p-6 shadow-sm transition-all duration-200 hover:shadow-md">
                    <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 mb-2">Subscription plan</span>
                    <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2 mb-4">
                        <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">{{ price }}</span>
                        <span class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">/month</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 flex-grow">
                        Launch a modern, branded storefront powered by Marketerum. Automate purchases, keep pricing in
                        sync, and manage your community from one intuitive dashboard.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Benefits List -->
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">What you get</h3>
                    <ul class="space-y-4">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <span class="flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary-500/10 dark:bg-primary-500/20 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true">
                                <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                                </svg>
                            </span>
                            <div class="flex-1">
                                <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-1">Ready-to-sell storefront</p>
                                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Connect your domain and start accepting orders
                                    instantly on every device.</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <span class="flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary-500/10 dark:bg-primary-500/20 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true">
                                <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                                </svg>
                            </span>
                            <div class="flex-1">
                                <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-1">Automated service syncing</p>
                                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Keep your catalogue aligned with the main panel
                                    without manual updates.</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <span class="flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary-500/10 dark:bg-primary-500/20 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true">
                                <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                                </svg>
                            </span>
                            <div class="flex-1">
                                <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-1">Client management tools</p>
                                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Monitor performance, unlock admin access, and stay
                                    on top of renewals with smart alerts.</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Child Panel Content -->
            {% if childpanel %}
            <div
                class="rounded-2xl border border-dashed border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-dark-card p-5 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 {% if site['rtl'] %} rtl-content {% endif %}">
                {{ childpanel }}
            </div>
            {% endif %}

            <!-- Order Form -->
            {% if showForm %}
            <form action="{{ page['url'] }}" method="post" class="space-y-6">
                {% if errorForm %}
                <div class="relative rounded-xl border border-red-200 dark:border-red-900/50 bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/20 p-4 text-red-800 dark:text-red-300 {% if site['rtl'] %} rtl-alert {% endif %}">
                    <button type="button" class="absolute top-2 right-2 text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 hover:text-red-800 dark:hover:text-red-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-500 rounded-lg p-1 transition-colors" data-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close">&times;</button>
                    {{ errorFormMessage }}
                </div>
                {% endif %}

                <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
                    <div class="space-y-2 md:col-span-2">
                        <label for="domain" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
                            {{ lang('child_panel.form.domain') }}
                        </label>
                        <input type="text" 
                            class="form-control w-full rounded-lg border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 bg-white dark:bg-dark-card px-4 py-2.5 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 placeholder-gray-400 dark:placeholder-gray-500 focus:border-primary-500 dark:focus:border-primary-400 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500/20 dark:focus:ring-primary-400/20 transition-colors" 
                            id="domain" 
                            name="CreateOrderForm[domain]"
                            value="{{ form['domain'] }}"
                            placeholder="example.com">
                    </div>

                    <div class="md:col-span-2">
                        <div class="rounded-xl border border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-900/50 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 p-4">
                            <div class="font-semibold text-blue-900 dark:text-blue-200 mb-2">{{ lang('child_panel.form.ns.info') }}</div>
                            <ul class="pl-5 list-disc space-y-1 text-sm text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-300">
                                {% for ns in name_servers %}
                                <li>{{ ns }}</li>
                                {% endfor %}
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="space-y-2">
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
                            for="createorderform-currency">{{ lang('child_panel.form.currency') }}</label>
                        <select id="createorderform-currency" 
                            class="form-control w-full rounded-lg border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 bg-white dark:bg-dark-card px-4 py-2.5 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 focus:border-primary-500 dark:focus:border-primary-400 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500/20 dark:focus:ring-primary-400/20 transition-colors" 
                            name="CreateOrderForm[currency]"
                            aria-required="true">
                            {% for currency in currenciesList %}
                            <option value="{{ currency['code'] }}" {% if form['currency'] == currency['code'] %}
                                selected{% endif %}>
                                {{ currency['name'] }}
                            </option>
                            {% endfor %}
                        </select>
                    </div>

                    <div class="space-y-2">
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
                            for="createorderform-username">{{ lang('child_panel.form.username') }}</label>
                        <input type="text" 
                            id="createorderform-username" 
                            class="form-control w-full rounded-lg border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 bg-white dark:bg-dark-card px-4 py-2.5 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 placeholder-gray-400 dark:placeholder-gray-500 focus:border-primary-500 dark:focus:border-primary-400 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500/20 dark:focus:ring-primary-400/20 transition-colors"
                            name="CreateOrderForm[username]" 
                            aria-required="true" 
                            value="{{ form['username'] }}"
                            placeholder="Username">
                    </div>

                    <div class="space-y-2">
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
                            for="createorderform-password">{{ lang('child_panel.form.password') }}</label>
                        <input type="password" 
                            id="createorderform-password" 
                            class="form-control w-full rounded-lg border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 bg-white dark:bg-dark-card px-4 py-2.5 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 placeholder-gray-400 dark:placeholder-gray-500 focus:border-primary-500 dark:focus:border-primary-400 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500/20 dark:focus:ring-primary-400/20 transition-colors"
                            name="CreateOrderForm[password]" 
                            aria-required="true"
                            placeholder="Password">
                    </div>

                    <div class="space-y-2">
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
                            for="createorderform-password_confirm">{{ lang('child_panel.form.confirm') }}</label>
                        <input type="password" 
                            id="createorderform-password_confirm" 
                            class="form-control w-full rounded-lg border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 bg-white dark:bg-dark-card px-4 py-2.5 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 placeholder-gray-400 dark:placeholder-gray-500 focus:border-primary-500 dark:focus:border-primary-400 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500/20 dark:focus:ring-primary-400/20 transition-colors"
                            name="CreateOrderForm[password_confirm]" 
                            aria-required="true"
                            placeholder="Confirm password">
                    </div>

                    <div class="space-y-2 md:col-span-2">
                        <label for="price" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
                            {{ lang('child_panel.form.price') }}
                        </label>
                        <input type="text" 
                            class="form-control w-full rounded-lg border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-dark-tertiary px-4 py-2.5 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 cursor-not-allowed" 
                            id="price" 
                            value="{{ price }}" 
                            readonly>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="{{ csrftoken }}">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn--primary w-full">
                    {{ lang('child_panel.form.submit') }}
                </button>
            </form>
            {% endif %}
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section class="my-24">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
            <div class="mx-auto mb-12 space-y-8 md:w-8/12">
                <span class="relative inline-block text-3xl font-bold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-500 to-primary-600 dark:from-primary-400 dark:to-primary-500">
                    F.A.Q
                    <img class="absolute -top-6 left-[110%] w-12 hidden lg:block" 
                        src="https://storage.perfectcdn.com/7gc9nb/7bklbfqr92dm1afi.png" 
                        alt=""
                        aria-hidden="true">
                </span>
            </div>

            <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
                <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
                    <!-- FAQ Item 1 -->
                    <div class="faq-item bg-white dark:bg-dark-secondary rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-sm overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-md">
                        <button type="button" class="faq-question w-full flex items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-dark-card transition-colors" aria-expanded="false">
                            <span>What is a Child Panel?</span>
                            <svg class="faq-icon h-5 w-5 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                <path d="M9 17V9M9 9V1M9 9H17M9 9H1" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </button>
                        <div class="faq-answer hidden px-5 pb-5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
                            A child panel is a smaller version of the main SMM panel. It allows users to resell social
                            media services like followers, likes, and views. You can buy a child panel and offer these
                            services at your own prices, making it easier to manage clients and orders.
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- FAQ Item 2 -->
                    <div class="faq-item bg-white dark:bg-dark-secondary rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-sm overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-md">
                        <button type="button" class="faq-question w-full flex items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-dark-card transition-colors" aria-expanded="false">
                            <span>How Does a Child Panel Benefit Me?</span>
                            <svg class="faq-icon h-5 w-5 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                <path d="M9 17V9M9 9V1M9 9H17M9 9H1" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </button>
                        <div class="faq-answer hidden px-5 pb-5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
                            By using a child panel, you can easily start your own business in social media services. You
                            can set your own prices, manage customer orders, and earn profit by reselling services. It's
                            perfect for freelancers or small businesses that want to grow.
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- FAQ Item 3 -->
                    <div class="faq-item bg-white dark:bg-dark-secondary rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-sm overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-md">
                        <button type="button" class="faq-question w-full flex items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-dark-card transition-colors" aria-expanded="false">
                            <span>Is a Child Panel Good for Beginners?</span>
                            <svg class="faq-icon h-5 w-5 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                <path d="M9 17V9M9 9V1M9 9H17M9 9H1" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </button>
                        <div class="faq-answer hidden px-5 pb-5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
                            Yes, child panels are easy to use and perfect for beginners. You don't need any special
                            skills to start reselling social media services. Everything is set up for you, so you can
                            focus on growing your business and managing your clients.
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- FAQ Item 4 -->
                    <div class="faq-item bg-white dark:bg-dark-secondary rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-sm overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-md">
                        <button type="button" class="faq-question w-full flex items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-dark-card transition-colors" aria-expanded="false">
                            <span>Can I Customize My Child Panel?</span>
                            <svg class="faq-icon h-5 w-5 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                <path d="M9 17V9M9 9V1M9 9H17M9 9H1" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </button>
                        <div class="faq-answer hidden px-5 pb-5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
                            Yes, you can customize your child panel by setting your own prices for the services you
                            offer. You can also manage how your clients place their orders and keep track of everything
                            in one place.
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- FAQ Item 5 -->
                    <div class="faq-item bg-white dark:bg-dark-secondary rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-sm overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-md">
                        <button type="button" class="faq-question w-full flex items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-dark-card transition-colors" aria-expanded="false">
                            <span>Are Child Panels Affordable?</span>
                            <svg class="faq-icon h-5 w-5 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                <path d="M9 17V9M9 9V1M9 9H17M9 9H1" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </button>
                        <div class="faq-answer hidden px-5 pb-5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
                            Yes, child panels are usually very affordable. You can start offering social media services
                            at low prices, making it a cost-effective way to enter the business. This makes them ideal
                            for anyone looking to start small and grow over time.
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- FAQ Item 6 -->
                    <div class="faq-item bg-white dark:bg-dark-secondary rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-sm overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-md">
                        <button type="button" class="faq-question w-full flex items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-dark-card transition-colors" aria-expanded="false">
                            <span>What Kind of Support is Available for Child Panels?</span>
                            <svg class="faq-icon h-5 w-5 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                <path d="M9 17V9M9 9V1M9 9H17M9 9H1" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </button>
                        <div class="faq-answer hidden px-5 pb-5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
                            We offer full support for child panel users. If you run into any issues or need help setting
                            up, you can easily reach our support team for assistance. It's a simple way to get started
                            with your own reselling business.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>